data.description: Welcome to this stunning 2-story West Jordan home situated in a desirable semi cul-de-sac with an open front porch. The formal living room features a large picture window, allowing natural light to flood the space. As you move through the open floor plan, you'll find the heart of this home lies in the family/dining/kitchen area. The family room is a true showstopper with its vaulted ceilings, floor-to-ceiling windows, and a cozy gas fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for those chilly winter nights. Connected to the family room is the semi-formal dining room and a chef's kitchen that will delight any culinary enthusiast. Equipped with a gas range (and wired for an electric range), a large island with bar seating, granite countertops and an abundance of cabinets, this kitchen is a dream come true. The main floor master suite is a retreat, offering tall ceilings, a bay window that fills the room with an abundance of natural light and views of the majestic mountains. The en-suite bathroom offers ultimate relaxation with his and her sinks, jetted tub, tiled shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. Venturing upstairs, you'll discover a loft area, perfect for a playroom, home office, or a cozy reading nook and dry bar. There are also four guest bedrooms that cater to everyone's needs, along with a full bathroom. The impressive fourth bedroom features a semi-vaulted ceiling, adding a unique architectural element. The basement is unfinished and waiting for your ideas and personal touch. With plenty of space for a great room/theater room and additional bedrooms. A spacious laundry room, complete with ample cabinet and counter space, is located just off the 4 car garage, the third car is a 2 car tandem, providing plenty of room for all your vehicles, and the gated RV parking offers an added bonus for those with adventurous spirits. Step outside to the fully fenced backyard, where you'll find yourself in your own private oasis with mountain views and quaking aspen trees. The raised garden beds are thoughtfully equipped with a drip system, making gardening a breeze. And for those nights of relaxation, gather around the fire pit. The 12 x 12 shed is perfect for all your gardening storage needs. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this place home. Call us today for your private showing.
